{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[G]Once in my youth I stood [C]on this [G]mountain
[D7]And planted some pines in the [G]sand
[C]Every day I looked their [G]way
[D7]But just couldn't [G]understand
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
