[A7]I just couldn't understand [D7]why
[G]Now I've rambled around this [C]wide world [G]through
[D7]And today I just happened [G]by
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 3}
[C]Tall pines tall pines
[G]Reaching up for the [D7]clouds
[G]Tall pines tall [C]pines
[G]I bet you wouldn't [D7]know me [G]now
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 4}
